description: NEWLY RENOVATED! A rare offering in one of South Boston’s most coveted neighborhoods, this fully renovated 4 bedroom, 3 bath home blends the sophistication of modern city living with the comfort and privacy of a single family residence. Thoughtfully reimagined from top to bottom, every detail has been elevated—from new electrical and plumbing systems to energy-efficient windows, exterior siding, and a high-performance heat pump with new hot water tank. The heart of the this home is the showstopping kitchen, where waterfall quartz countertops extend to a matching backsplash, complemented by sleek white cabinetry, elegant gold hardware, stainless steel appliances, and a farmer's sink. Sunlit living spaces are enriched by gleaming hardwood floors, recessed lighting, and a seamless flow designed for both entertaining and everyday comfort. With a prime location near Southie’s best restaurants, shops, parks, and beaches, this turn-key home is ready for its new owners.
